# === BillBuffer repo hygiene ===
# This repo is documentation-only today. These rules guard the privacy promise:
# nothing personal, and no disposable prototype code, may be committed.

# --- Personal / disposable prototype (NEVER commit) ---
# The prototype is a disposable UX + calculation test model that embedded personal
# seed data (real bills, balances, APRs). It is local-only by design.
billbuffer-prototype.html
billbuffer-prototype-notes.md
*prototype*.html

# --- User data exports / backups / seeds (may contain personal financial data) ---
*seed*.json
*backup*.json
billbuffer-backup.json
*-backup.json
*.seed.json
*.local.json
exports/
backups/
user_data/

# --- Dependencies ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Environment variables ---
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- IDE / OS junk ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Build outputs (for when production starts) ---
.svelte-kit/
dist/
build/
*.log
.cache/
.vercel/
.netlify/

# --- Security — never commit these ---
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/

# --- Local development ---
*.local
